Uses of Package
com.invectorate.open.queutures

  • Classes in com.invectorate.open.queutures used by com.invectorate.open.queutures 
    Class and Description
    Informable
    An object that performs an abitrary computation when it is given input of a certain type.
    Queuture
    A representation of the outcome of an arbitrary asynchronous computation that may generate many results.
    QueutureBox
    The opaque interface that Informables that are expected to be used to generate data for Queutures use to submit new information.
    QueutureExecutorService
    An ExecutorService that also supports submitting instances of Informable to create Queutures.
    RunnableQueuture
    A Queuture that can itself be executed as a Runnable.
